# The 100-name subset of the 252 above that CPython's `html5` dict ALSO
# lists WITHOUT a trailing `;` (python3.12.9-verified exact set — the
# "legacy SGML" entities: `amp`, `lt`, `gt`, `quot`, `copy`, `nbsp`, `not`,
# accented Latin-1 letters, etc.). The other 152 names in
# `_html_name2codepoint` require the trailing `;` (matches CPython).
